author: Amy Furr
title: Report: Connecticut Birthday Party Became Coronavirus ‘Super-Spreading Event’
description: Over half of a woman's 50 party guests tested positive for the Chinese coronavirus following the celebration on March 5 in Westport, Connecticut.
content:
